      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 26.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 26.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>雖有榮觀，燕處超然。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Although he may have brilliant prospects to look at, he quietly remains (in his proper place), indifferent to them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-026__align-004">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
