      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 26.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 26.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>輕則失本，躁則失君。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>If he do act lightly, he has lost his root (of gravity); if he proceed to active movement, he will lose his throne.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
